---

This package bundles parser sources generated by GNU Bison
(src/_sgl/parser.tab.c, src/_sgl/parser.tab.h), which embed the Bison parser
skeleton. That skeleton is copyright (C) the Free Software Foundation, Inc. The
original copyright notice and the Bison special-exception license are preserved
verbatim within those files, and that exception permits distribution of the
generated parser under this package's license.
